---
title: Flank Steak & Zesty Parsley Butter with Hasselback Kumara & Parmesan Green Bean Salad
description: Steak night is back and better than ever! It’s flank steak tonight, tender and juicy, with a dollop of zesty parsley compound butter on top. We’ve got a fun kumara side as well; our hasselback technique offers the ultimate combo of crispy, fluffy and
flavour-packed!
This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.
